      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRESIDENT ROLEX (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.66 beating Billy Ray's Girl. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. The hardest to beat again. MAGIC BANDIT (4) hit the ground running from the squeeze draw with a fast early split last time, but run over late and missed the frame when a 3 length fourth (30.02) over 520m at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Should be in this for a long way. OVERFLOW BEAU (2) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 2 lengths back in third (30.05) at this track in a Mix 1/2/3 over 520m. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from six starts. Well placed and gets his chance. ZIPPING HOPKINS (7) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
